nakita ART babai OBL lalaki
saw the girl the boy
`The girl saw the boy'

# Ex. 17: incorrect agent NP case with transitive verb: tr oblique-NP core-NP
Source: a:32
Vetted: s
Judgment: u
Phenomena: {c}
Nakita iti babai ti lalaki
nakita OBL babai ART lalaki
saw the girl the boy
`The girl saw the boy'

# Ex. 18: too many core-NP after transitive verb
Source: a:32
Vetted: s
Judgment: u
Phenomena: {argument optionality}
Nakita iti babai ti lalaki ti babai
nakita OBL babai ART lalaki ART babai
saw the girl the boy the girl
`The girl saw the boy'

# Ex. 19: incorrect det-noun order for NPs with transitive verb
Source: a:32
Vetted: s
Judgment: u
Phenomena: {argument optionality}
Nakita babai ti ti lalaki
nakita babai ART ART lalaki
saw girl the the boy
`The girl saw the boy'

# Ex. 20: incorrect det-noun order for NPs with transitive verb
Source: a:32
Vetted: s
Judgment: u
Phenomena: {argument optionality}
Nakita ti babai lalaki ti
nakita ART babai lalaki ART
saw the girl boy the
`The girl saw the boy'

# Ex. 21: incorrect det-noun order for NPs with transitive verb
Source: a:32
Vetted: s
Judgment: u
Phenomena: {argument optionality}
Nakita ti babai lalaki ti
nakita babai ART lalaki ART
saw girl the boy the
`The girl saw the boy'

